    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\begin{aligned}\nOM^2 &= (5-t)^2 + (5-t)^2 + (7-2t)^2 = 50 - 20t + 2t^2 + 49 - 28t + 4t^2 \\\\\n&= 99 - 48t + 6t^2 = 6(t^2 - 8t + 16) + 3 = 6(t-4)^2 + 3 \\ge 3\n\\end{aligned}\n$$"
